3b24368dc2ef16bf89af038cce2a09d72a7a","tid":1182042,"uid":124146,"like":40,"dislike":19,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T01:53:36.000Z","msg":"英超就全世界最高水平聯賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T02:40:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得係<br />\n其中一個主要原因<br />\n係全球整體球員嘅腳法比起二三十年前明顯退步咗<br />\n英超球隊普遍注重速度體能<br />\n喺以前面對意／西／德甲勁旅時<br />\n呢啲快速行軍／攔截就好容易俾啲好腳法嘅球隊打開空位兼打殘<br />\n但今時唔同往日<br />\n當英超前列嗰幾隊波，面對而家其他歐洲聯賽列強時<br />\n對手係唔夠腳法同速率壓制住佢哋<br />\n尤其當佢哋運用壓逼性打法時，就更難應對<br />\n再加上，英超比賽嘅官能刺激同比賽節奏<br />\n更加令全球更多人觀看，從而賺取更多轉播費<br />\n繼而就有更多錢買人同吸引最好嗰班球員入嚟英超<br />\n窮者就越窮，富者就越富"},{"pid":"abdfb7a273e915f17cb7cb995d36845f69e068ab","tid":1182042,"uid":12355,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"9c4f3b24368dc2ef16bf89af038cce2a09d72a7a","tid":1182042,"uid":124146,"like":40,"dislike":19,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T01:53:36.000Z","msg":"英超就全世界最高水平聯賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"唔係英超咁邊個聯賽最佳？<br />\n今年應該係英超最佳啦<br />\n歐聯歐霸決賽四隊英超<br />\n你唔認同？"},{"pid":"ad6760b50176156da26d432cdba481fb5b418fa3","tid":1182042,"uid":116643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T03:02:15.000Z","msg":"係屋企睇電腦威<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3456d91e8f1b6dff3260d0ce33a0c5a55dd0c3","tid":1182042,"uid":250502,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"我地曼聯拎到咩咪咩威d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c40dd49d867f2d9c116be46df6945356710b7a","tid":1182042,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T03:11:03.000Z","msg":"歐聯啦"},{"pid":"3142823cefcb1d935e54192d8a1ced077a500b90","tid":1182042,"uid":174940,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"abdfb7a273e915f17cb7cb995d36845f69e068ab","tid":1182042,"uid":12355,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"quote